---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 121
By: St Alphonsus Liguori
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Sacrifice and Suffering=The Divine Allopathy
  - Discernment-Truth=Reality=The Nature of Reality
---
We must not attribute our losses, misfortunes, sufferings and humiliations to
the evil spirit or to man; but to their true author, God.
